Billion Dollar Secret



Company Summary
BiondVax Pharmaceuticals Ltd. is a biopharmaceutical company. The company's product includes Multimeric-001 universal flu vaccine which provides multi-season and multi-strain protection against human influenza virus strains. BiondVax Pharmaceuticals Ltd. is based in Ness Ziona, Israel.   

















 





























